| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4604 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ce55ffa0-8ae9-5526-9def-a51d46b06ec2"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
